                  <provenance>Copied for አቡነ፡ ገብረ፡ ማርያም and the members of መካነ፡ ሕይወት, fol. 11v, 14r, 29v; Written in memory of ወልደ፡ ሚካኤል and his family, fol. 11v and throughout; Purchased from the monastery of ገዳመ፡ ጭሐ፡ መካነ፡ ሕይወት by Empress Zawditu and she gave it to Trinity Church, መካነ፡ ሥላሴ, in 1911 EC (1918/1919), fol. 122v; Original colophon has been erased, fol. 122v; Seal of Qeddest Śellāsē Cathedral, fol. 4r, 122v; Seal of Empress Zawditu, fol. 122v
                     
